{"tid":1729220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油尖旺紅土開花救埋土","createTime":"2019-11-17T06:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T09:42:54.000Z","uid":125627,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2cbbbe4b068985729c0b7ad5e1558189cfc5cefe","tid":1729220,"uid":125627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:56:36.000Z","msg":"💥 開花裝修圍魏救趙呀​💥 等理大​手足安全撤走💥<br />\n<br />\n#手足投稿 （轉發）<br />\n<br />\n在解放軍軍語中叫做「圍點打援」，是指以部分兵力包圍城市或要點，誘敵增援，集中主力殲滅援敵於運動中。目的不在於打被圍之敵，而在於打援敵。世界上恐怕沒有哪支軍隊能像我人民解放軍一樣將這種戰術運用得如此爐火純青，特別是在波瀾壯闊的解放戰爭中，各大戰場都留下了「圍城打援」的經典之作，國民黨軍五大主力中有兩個被殲於此。<br />\n<br />\n我講咗啲咩自己諗<br />\n去咗好多紅磚嘅地方接人走 但係原來佢哋係要守喺嗰度， 我理解佢哋想視死如歸 但係戰略上我根本睇唔到齊上齊落 be water 想救都救唔到 因為根本唔畀你救 好心痛 怪唔得警察唔攻入去 留住個春袋就大把人入去"},{"pid":"a5f14d23b7d04e6a51a06152e02c6088ecb38ad7","tid":1729220,"uid":5801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0453bb6a429e56ad6ff58f74d29d8b990a10baf","tid":1729220,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:56:58.000Z","msg":"警察砲轟poly，要推畀國際知！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter 組不斷更新 Task3</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=713eabed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">/task3</span></span>就得！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有一定要響外國議員/名人/外媒關於香港的tweets reply Poly最新情況，向國際求救</span><br />\n<br />\n！！！眾志：解放軍拎自動步槍同刺刀<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/demosisto/status/1195948090118721536?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%